result.adr_address: 54號 Peel St, Central, Hong Kong
result.name: Roastery Lab By The Coffee Academics

reviews.text:
Good place to work! 
Accessible as it is near to the Sheung Wan MTR station.

Thumbs up for the enjoyable experiece .. both Anson & Suki were great .. sampled diff grades .. and took their "coffee compatibility test" .. and came away w a really flavourful "smoky" coffee, the way i like it .. i walked past this place several times, & stopped by (on my last day, just hrs b4 departing for the airport) .. just wished tt they had seats available, so can chill & sip away whilst taking in the aroma ...
Great venue. It’s worth the walk up hill to get to this place. Filter here is spot on
now is 18:35 but it's closed.  opening hour on the door is 10am-7pm daily.
best nicaragua ever.
